author: Herald Staff
title: New Democratic N.H. presidential poll at 9:30 a.m. on Boston Herald Radio
text:
How’s Hillary Clinton doing against Bernie Sanders — and where will Joe Biden stand if he jumps in?
Tune into Boston Herald Radio today at 9:30 a.m. when the results in the latest Franklin Pierce University/ Boston Herald poll of New Hampshire’s Democratic presidential primary campaign will be released live on air.
